, England":"영국 요르크실르","lifeSummary":"Hugh de Aske(이)가 1240년 이전 영국 잉글랜드 요르크실르 이스비 아스크에서 태어났을 때, 그의 아버지 Roger de Aske(은)는 11236세였고, 그의 어머니 Margaret of England(은)는 40세였다. 그는 영국 요르크실르 이스비 아스크에서 Cecilia of England(와)과 결혼했다. 그들은 적어도 네 명의 아들을 두었다. 그는 영국 잉글랜드 요르크실르에서 사망했다."},"lv":{"before 1240–":"pirms 1240. gada–miris","1240–Male":"1240–miris","1248–Male":"1248–miris","1288–Male":"1288.gads–miris","1290–Male":"1290–miris","1240–1304":"1240–1304","1280–Male":"1280.gads–miris","1284–1335":"1284.gads–1335","1286–Male":"1286.gads–miris","1200–1280":"1200–1280.gads","1200–Female":"1200–mirusi","about 1280":"ap 1280. gadu","1286":"1286. gads","1285":"1285. gads","1284":"1284. gads","1240":"1240","1280":"1280. gads","<1286>":"1286. gads","1290":"1290","1304":"1304","1248":"1248","1335":"1335","1288":"1288. gads","1200":"1200","before 1240":"pirms 1240. gada","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, Anglija, Lielbritānija","Aske, Easby, Yorkshire, England":"Aske, Easby, Yorkshire, England","Aske Manor, Yorkshire, England":"Manor, Yorkshire, England","Wele-juxta-Beverley, Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England"},"mg":{"before 1240–":"talohan'ny 1240–Maty","1240–Male":"1240–Maty","1248–Male":"1248–Maty","1288–Male":"1288–Maty","1290–Male":"1290–Maty","1240–1304":"1240–1304","1280–Male":"1280–Maty","1284–1335":"1284–1335","1286–Male":"1286–Maty","1200–1280":"1200–1280","1200–Female":"1200–Maty","about 1280":"tany ho any amin'ny 1280","1286":"1286","1285":"1285","1284":"1284","1240":"1240","1280":"1280","<1286>":"1286","1290":"1290","1304":"1304","1248":"1248","1335":"1335","1288":"1288","1200":"1200","before 1240":"talohan'ny 1240","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, Angletera, United Kingdom","Aske, Easby, Yorkshire, England":"Aske, Easby, Yorkshire, England","Aske Manor, Yorkshire, England":"Manor, Yorkshire, England","Wele-juxta-Beverley, Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England"},"ms":{"before 1240–":"sebelum 1240–Mati","1240–Male":"1240–Mati","1248–Male":"1248–Mati","1288–Male":"1288–Mati"